700k+ followers and this reply ⬇️🤌🏻

We’re all inspired by each other in small, beautiful ways. Sometimes we know it, sometimes we don’t. Sujata has draped sarees in so many different styles, and we’re always in awe when amazing women send us videos of how they’ve made it their own.
At Suta, we’ve always believed there’s no such thing as a “shabby” or “proper” drape you should wear what makes you feel good.
Ta draped hers in five minutes, and she felt happy and that’s all that matters.
And honestly, whether it’s Suta Bombay with 758k followers or just one passionate creator, we’re all just humans behind a screen, learning, exploring, and celebrating sarees in our own way.
So here’s to giving credit where it’s due you’re doing an amazing job. Keep going, girl.

Feeling so blessed! 🤌🏻🧿
